contentrichtext.text: {{archive}} ''This page is an archive of the discussion surrounding the proposed deletion of the page entitled [[Literati]]. This page is kept as an historic record. The result of the debate was to keep as a redirect to [[Intellectual]].''' ---- * Dicdef. Delete. [[User:Pteron|Pteron]] 00:58, 11 May 2004 (UTC) * Move to wikipedia? [[User:Alcarillo|Alcarillo]] 14:04, 11 May 2004 (UTC) **You mean wiktionary? I guess it could be transwikied, but it's not exactly a great definition... [[User:Pteron|Pteron]] 22:24, 11 May 2004 (UTC) *No, just tag this onto the existing [[intellectual]] page - would be in place there. In fact, why don't I just merge it in and redirect? [[User:Charles Matthews|Charles Matthews]] 09:26, 16 May 2004 (UTC) **'''K'''eep now that the redirect is done. --[[User:Zigger|Zigger]] 21:10, 2004 May 16 (UTC) ---- This page is now preserved as an archive of the debate and is no longer 'live'. Subsequent comments on the issue should be placed on other relevant 'live' pages. '''Please do not edit this page.''' ----
